"title": "2363: Jesus Christ, preaching and teaching of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2363: jesus christ, preaching and teaching of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A vital feature of Jesus Christ's ministry, focusing on his authoritative proclamation of the kingdom of God.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mission as preaching and teaching</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:43\">LUK 4:43</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:38\">MRK 1:38</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:5\">MAT 11:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:22\">LUK 7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:6\">MRK 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:16\">JHN 7:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:1\">ACT 1:1</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ was regarded as a teacher and prophet</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:38\">JHN 1:38</a></strong> <em>“Rabbi” was an honorific title given to Jesus Christ unofficially by the people.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:14\">MAT 16:14</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:28\">MRK 8:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:19\">LUK 9:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:10\">MAT 23:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:25\">MAT 26:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:5\">MRK 9:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:51\">MRK 10:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:13\">JHN 13:13</a></p>\n<h2>The sources of Jesus Christ's preaching and teaching</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's words were grounded in Scripture</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:27\">LUK 24:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:4\">MAT 4:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:4\">LUK 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">DEU 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:16\">MAT 21:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:2\">PSA 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:29-Matt22:32\">MAT 22:29–22:32</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:24-Mark12:27\">MRK 12:24–12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:35-Luke20:38\">LUK 20:35–20:38</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's words came from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:16\">JHN 7:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:2\">JHN 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:28\">JHN 8:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:49-John12:50\">JHN 12:49–12:50</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ spoke in the power of the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:2\">ACT 1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:14-Luke4:15\">LUK 4:14–4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:34\">JHN 3:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:63\">JHN 6:63</a></p>\n<h2>The content of Jesus Christ's preaching and teaching</h2>\n<h3>The kingdom of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:11\">LUK 9:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:17\">MAT 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:23\">MAT 4:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:33\">MAT 6:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:24\">MAT 13:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:15\">MRK 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:3\">JHN 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>God as Father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:8-John14:14\">JHN 14:8–14:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:31-Matt6:32\">MAT 6:31–6:32</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:30-Luke12:31\">LUK 12:30–12:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:32-Matt10:33\">MAT 10:32–10:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:10\">MAT 18:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:25\">MRK 11:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:17-John5:23\">JHN 5:17–5:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:18-John8:19\">JHN 8:18–8:19</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's own identity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:25-John4:26\">JHN 4:25–4:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:13-Matt16:17\">MAT 16:13–16:17</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:27-Mark8:30\">MRK 8:27–8:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:18-Luke9:21\">LUK 9:18–9:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:20-Luke4:21\">LUK 4:20–4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:44\">LUK 24:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:11\">JHN 10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6-John14:7\">JHN 14:6–14:7</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's mission</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:31\">MRK 9:31</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:22-Matt17:23\">MAT 17:22–17:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:44\">LUK 9:44</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:17-Matt20:19\">MAT 20:17–20:19</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:32-Mark10:34\">MRK 10:32–10:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:31-Luke18:34\">LUK 18:31–18:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:9-Luke19:10\">LUK 19:9–19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:46\">LUK 24:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:51\">JHN 6:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:14-John10:15\">JHN 10:14–10:15</a></p>\n<h3>How people should live</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:20-Matt5:22\">MAT 5:20–5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:43-Matt5:44\">MAT 5:43–5:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:12\">MAT 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21-Matt19:24\">MAT 19:21–19:24</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:21-Mark10:25\">MRK 10:21–10:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:22-Luke18:25\">LUK 18:22–18:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:35-Matt22:40\">MAT 22:35–22:40</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:28-Mark12:31\">MRK 12:28–12:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:35\">LUK 6:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34-John13:35\">JHN 13:34–13:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:12-John15:13\">JHN 15:12–15:13</a></p>\n<h3>The future</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:62\">MRK 14:62</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:69\">LUK 22:69</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:15\">MAT 10:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:12\">LUK 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:36-Matt12:37\">MAT 12:36–12:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:1-Matt24:2\">MAT 24:1–24:2</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:1-Mark13:2\">MRK 13:1–13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:5-Luke21:6\">LUK 21:5–21:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:36-Matt24:44\">MAT 24:36–24:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31-Matt25:33\">MAT 25:31–25:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:26-Luke17:35\">LUK 17:26–17:35</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ criticised false teachings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:6-Matt15:9\">MAT 15:6–15:9</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:6-Mark7:7\">MRK 7:6–7:7</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:15-Matt7:16\">MAT 7:15–7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:12\">MAT 16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:2-Matt23:4\">MAT 23:2–23:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:38-Mark12:39\">MRK 12:38–12:39</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:45-Luke20:46\">LUK 20:45–20:46</a></p>\n<h2>The results of Jesus Christ's preaching and teaching</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ invited a response</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28-Matt11:30\">MAT 11:28–11:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:23\">MAT 13:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:20\">MRK 4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:15\">LUK 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:8-Matt22:10\">MAT 22:8–22:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:21-Luke14:24\">LUK 14:21–14:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ looked for an obedient response</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:28\">LUK 11:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:24-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:24–7:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:15\">MAT 11:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:23\">MAT 13:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:20\">MRK 4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:15\">LUK 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:20\">MAT 28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:9\">MRK 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23-John14:24\">JHN 14:23–14:24</a></p>\n<h3>People responded to Jesus Christ's preaching and teaching</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:42\">JHN 12:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:19-Matt8:22\">MAT 8:19–8:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:57-Luke9:60\">LUK 9:57–9:60</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:10-Matt13:15\">MAT 13:10–13:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:10-Mark4:12\">MRK 4:10–4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:39\">JHN 4:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:68-John6:69\">JHN 6:68–6:69</a></p>\n<h2>Characteristics of Jesus Christ's preaching and teaching</h2>\n<h3>It had authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:28-Matt7:29\">MAT 7:28–7:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:23\">MAT 21:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:28\">MRK 11:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:2\">LUK 20:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:22\">MAT 22:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:17\">MRK 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:26\">LUK 20:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:22\">MRK 1:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:32\">LUK 4:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:27\">MRK 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:15\">JHN 7:15</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ lived out what he preached and taught</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:38\">JHN 10:38</a></strong> <em>The “miracles” (literally “works”) conveyed the same message as Jesus Christ's words.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:29\">MAT 11:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24\">MAT 16:24</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34\">MRK 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23\">LUK 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:15\">JHN 13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34\">JHN 13:34</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's preaching and teaching methods</h2>\n<h3>His use of lessons drawn from people's experience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:16-Matt9:17\">MAT 9:16–9:17</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:21-Mark2:22\">MRK 2:21–2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:36-Luke5:37\">LUK 5:36–5:37</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:11-Matt12:12\">MAT 12:11–12:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:12\">MAT 18:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:4\">LUK 15:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:62\">LUK 9:62</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:15-Luke13:16\">LUK 13:15–13:16</a></p>\n<h3>His use of parables</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:34\">MAT 13:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:3\">MAT 13:3</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:2\">MRK 4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:4\">LUK 8:4</a></p>\n<h3>His use of everyday objects</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:26-Matt6:29\">MAT 6:26–6:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:23-Luke12:27\">LUK 12:23–12:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:19-Matt22:21\">MAT 22:19–22:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:15-Mark12:17\">MRK 12:15–12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:24-Luke20:25\">LUK 20:24–20:25</a></p>\n<h3>His use of questions</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:25-Matt6:28\">MAT 6:25–6:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:24-Matt21:25\">MAT 21:24–21:25</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:29\">MRK 11:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:3-Luke20:4\">LUK 20:3–20:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:36-Luke10:37\">LUK 10:36–10:37</a></p>",
